        "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nHi Akhila,\n\nThanks, that you will fix \"Pending\" case.\n\nIn case of this label \"issue\", thanks for your explaination.\nIn my example I didn't necessarily want to check OS version or other particular field, but just provide some label to affinity rule, that should always work if nfd is working, and fail it it's not.\nI've just took a look at your kernel version match rule and it looks much better.\nI'd suggest switching match operator from \"In\", \"4\" to \"Gt\", \"3\", so that it would also work for later kernel releases (https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/generated/kubernetes-api/v1.11/#nodeselectorrequirement-v1-core).",
